## Rotation Pressure — recent speakers and recent pairs

The single most common failure mode is the same pair bantering every tick with the same speaker each time. Use the list below to actively rotate AWAY from whoever just spoke.

{% set lastSpeakers = [] %}
{% set lastPairs = [] %}
{% for ev in pastTopics %}
{% if existsIn(ev.data, "speaker") and existsIn(ev.data, "listener") and ev.data.speaker != "" and ev.data.listener != "" %}
{% set lastSpeakers = append(lastSpeakers, ev.data.speaker) %}
{% set lastPairs = append(lastPairs, ev.data.speaker + " & " + ev.data.listener) %}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if length(lastSpeakers) > 0 %}
